and we will go straight down.

5
00:03:23,710 --> 00:03:28,599
We have still to cover 20 miles.
Bihari, why don't U drive faster.

6
00:03:28,763 --> 00:03:30,255
Why are you getting so restless?

7
00:03:30,825 --> 00:03:34,493
Why not? The car came late, and
we reach the station late, then...

8
00:03:34,557 --> 00:03:37,426
