have cleaned this.

132
00:21:56,848 --> 00:21:58,462
You seem quite tired.

133
00:21:59,261 --> 00:22:03,336
Why not drink a cup of tea?
- I don't need it. I'll get for you.

134
00:22:05,176 --> 00:22:09,226
You have come new here.

135
00:22:09,496 --> 00:22:12,536
