You have a long life.

139
00:22:20,749 --> 00:22:22,351
Hello Manager. - Hello.

140
00:22:22,483 --> 00:22:24,968
Enroute I hope you didn't
have any difficulty. - No.

141
00:22:25,009 --> 00:22:26,366
