still makes only her picture.

468
01:05:42,048 --> 01:05:44,579
And he keeps meeting
her near the spring.

469
01:06:10,929 --> 01:06:12,256
Are you in any hurry 
to go somewhere?

470
01:06:12,497 --> 01:06:14,404
Yes, my work has
finished for today. l...

