trying to steal my self respect?

656
01:36:29,234 --> 01:36:30,992
You lowly scoundrel! You wretch!

657
01:36:39,372 --> 01:36:44,183
Here! You can kill me, but don't 
make such cheap allegations.

658
01:36:44,454 --> 01:36:46,995
Such cheap and false acts is 
the religion of people like you.

659
01:36:47,200 --> 01:36:49,608
Sin is a part of your blood.

660
01:36:49,936 --> 01:36:52,693
There is no sin in my blood,
there is falseness in your vision.

661
01:36:52,820 --> 01:36:57,871
