before he comes back.

713
01:41:20,689 --> 01:41:23,750
Look I am going, 
and you smile a bit!

714
01:41:26,169 --> 01:41:29,677
Look.

715
01:41:33,163 --> 01:41:35,918
If you have to go, 
then come with me.

716
01:41:36,110 --> 01:41:38,426
Where? - To take
the Lord's blessings.

717
01:41:39,849 --> 01:41:41,739
Let's go. - Come.

718
01:42:29,074 --> 01:42:31,999
The flower fell!
- So what, if the flower fell?

719
01:42:32,960 --> 01:42:38,494
It is a very bad sign.
If one's flower falls, one dies!

720
01:42:39,016 --> 01:42:41,259
You are unnecessarily
saying bad things.

721
01:42:41,305 --> 01:42:48,476
No. I don't want to die. 
Before meeting you...

722
01:42:49,162 --> 01:42:51,282
I was not scared of death,

723
