02:14:10,035 --> 02:14:20,114
What the heart had gained,
have been lost by the eyes.

972
02:14:20,766 --> 02:14:28,908
Broken dreams have taught me...

973
02:14:29,450 --> 02:14:39,404
That what the heart gained,
have been lost by the eyes.

974
02:14:40,114 --> 02:14:44,185
The broken dreams...

975
02:14:57,395 --> 02:15:05,976
My appeals returned,
after striking the stars.

976
02:15:06,057 --> 02:15:14,429
My appeals returned,
after striking the stars.

977
02:15:14,693 --> 02:15:26,934
It returned from all corners
of devastated world of mine.

978
02:15:27,677 --> 02:15:35,803
But all this sorrow,
has been of no use...

979
02:15:36,214 --> 02:15:46,295
That what the heart gained,
have been lost by the eyes.

980
02:15:46,852 --> 02:15:51,520
The broken dreams...

981
02:16:23,045 --> 02:16:25,182
Does anyone by the
name of Anand stay here?

982
02:16:25,311 --> 02:16:29,165
What to say, he does and
also does not. I can't understand.

983
02:16:30,028 --> 02:16:34,149
I just make his food,
which I have to eat.

984
02:16:35,970 --> 02:16:39,534
Neither he or his servant is here.
Wait inside, one of them...

985
02:16:39,574 --> 02:16:42,706
...should be coming very soon.
Please sit inside.

986
02:16:50,855 --> 02:16:51,636
I am sorry.

987
02:16:54,190 --> 02:16:54,909
Listen.

988
02:16:54,994 --> 02:16:56,841
Don't talk to me.
- Why?

989
02:16:57,009 --> 02:16:58,444
You deprived thief!

990
02:16:58,560 --> 02:16:59,560
That must be your father!

991
02:16:59,600 --> 02:17:01,510
And your grandfather, great grand
father and all your fore fathers.

992
02:17:01,737 --> 02:17:03,331
Yesterday you let me down!

993
02:17:03,465 --> 02:17:05,944
Telling me about your Ghost removers.

994
02:17:06,107 --> 02:17:09,864
Show me the ghost, brink him in front of
me, or else I'll bring my you the ghost.

995
02:17:15,029 --> 02:17:17,622
Hello, What happened?

996
02:17:21,341 --> 02:17:22,052
Listen..

997
02:17:25,267 --> 02:17:30,323
Please forgive me, it was 
not my fault. Forgive me.

998
02:17:30,490 --> 02:17:33,904
I am scared of ghosts.
Forgive me, Madhu.

999
02:17:34,551 --> 02:17:36,383
I am not Madhu, but Madhavi.

1000
02:17:37,402 --> 02:17:40,925
Madhavi? Really?

1001
02:17:43,190 --> 02:17:50,356
Let me touch and confirm.
Yes! Same nose, same features.

1002
02:17:50,520 --> 02:17:57,059
...same eyes. So it is you, 
he mistook for Madhu.

1003
02:17:58,277 --> 02:18:03,797
Just tell me, who is Madhu?
What happened to her?

1004
02:18:04,465 --> 02:18:07,040
Please sit down.
I will tell you everything.

1005
02:18:20,699 --> 02:18:23,028
This is the story of this
unfortunate girl.

1006
02:18:23,921 --> 02:18:28,784
I am fairly sure she is dead.
But sir doesn't believe she is dead.

1007
02:18:29,434 --> 02:18:35,149
Now I know why on the hills,
he was calling for Madhu.

1008
02:18:37,411 --> 02:18:40,750
It is dark now. I will 
light the lamp and come.

1009
02:19:09,127 --> 02:19:10,197
Sir has come!

1010
02:19:49,122 --> 02:19:51,842
If there was any one else in my 
place, he would've been misled.

1011
02:20:27,110 --> 02:20:27,875
Anil sir.

1012
02:20:29,387 --> 02:20:31,954
You do not know what
injustice I have gone through.

1013
02:20:32,846 --> 02:20:36,102
I know, I have heard it all.

1014
02:20:41,575 --> 02:20:46,706
I feel as if Madhu's
sorrow has become mine.

1015
02:21:02,527 --> 02:21:04,327
Don't shed tears for me.

1016
02:21:09,652 --> 02:21:15,087
Same face, same eyes, same looks...

1017
02:21:29,705 --> 02:21:39,681
Come, my foreigner.

1018
02:21:42,417 --> 02:21:45,748
The darkness has set...

1019
02:21:46,108 --> 02:21:47,931
Are you hearing it? - What?

1020
02:21:49,497 --> 02:21:50,587
She is calling me...

1021
02:21:52,321 --> 02:21:53,558
Where are you going?

1022
02:21:54,751 --> 02:21:55,579
Madhu.

1023
02:21:59,102 --> 02:22:00,875
Madhu.

1024
02:22:03,798 --> 02:22:04,610
Madhu.

1025
02:22:09,267 --> 02:22:10,392
Madhu.

1026
02:22:11,575 --> 02:22:15,218
I stay close to you,
amongst the stars.

1027
02:22:15,927 --> 02:22:20,868
I had promised. I won, and he lost.

1028
02:22:21,352 --> 02:22:28,580
Who?- Wake up and see.
He has my blood on his hands.

1029
02:22:28,667 --> 02:22:32,156
Who has? - Ugra Narain.

1030
02:22:35,668 --> 02:22:37,894
That snake wanted to bite me.

1031
02:22:40,417 --> 02:22:42,667
Madhu, madhu.

1032
02:22:43,260 --> 02:22:44,026
Anil sir.

1033
02:22:49,675 --> 02:22:51,578
I am going.
- Where?

1034
02:22:52,763 --> 02:22:55,410
His hands are red
with my Madhu's blood.

1035
02:22:56,481 --> 02:23:00,225
And that snake is still alive.
- Whom are you talking of?

1036
02:23:00,335 --> 02:23:01,435
Ugra Narain.

1037
02:23:04,933 --> 02:23:07,996
I know this Ugra Narain.
He is quite a goon.

1038
02:23:08,483 --> 02:23:10,719
Earlier too he had a hand 
in two or three murders.

1039
02:23:11,180 --> 02:23:14,580
You know it, and yet this 
dangerous animal is free!

1040
02:23:15,326 --> 02:23:17,278
Why don't you arrest 
him, Inspector?

1041
02:23:17,326 --> 02:23:19,009
I have expressed my helplessness.

1042
02:23:20,326 --> 02:23:22,681
Without proof nothing can be done.

1043
02:23:24,687 --> 02:23:27,859
Hello. Hello Kamal, yes.

1044
02:23:29,668 --> 02:23:31,842
Madhavi's dance and 
I will not come?

1045
02:23:32,438 --> 02:23:36,495
There are still 15 minutes left.
I am reaching there straight away.

1046
02:23:37,002 --> 02:23:38,877
Yes, okay. See you.

1047
02:23:41,426 --> 02:23:43,970
Ok, if you don't have time,
I will take leave.

1048
02:23:44,922 --> 02:23:49,269
Wait. Leave the pistol here.
Bring it here.

1049
02:23:50,912 --> 02:23:53,256
Give me the pistol for just 2 days.

1050
02:23:53,865 --> 02:23:57,843
I will kill that sinner.
Later you can hang me.

1051
02:23:58,174 --> 02:24:02,499
My revenge will be complete.
- Don't be rash, keep the pistol.

1052
02:24:07,426 --> 02:24:13,294
Listen, if you want Madhu's
murderer punished, then produce...

1053
02:24:13,677 --> 02:24:17,427
...some solid proofs.
I assure you I will help you.

1054
02:24:19,710 --> 02:24:21,758
Where are you going? 
- I don't know.

1055
02:24:22,562 --> 02:24:24,094
Come with me. - Where?

1056
02:24:24,296 --> 02:24:25,296
Just come.

1057
02:24:41,056 --> 02:24:41,751
Hello.

1058
02:24:42,141 --> 02:24:45,254
Hello Inspector, you 
took quite some time.

1059
02:24:45,632 --> 02:24:47,915
Yes, some office matters
and we got delayed.

1060
02:26:01,346 --> 02:26:08,168
Oh, the scorpion!

1061
02:26:37,489 --> 02:26:45,947
The mantras are of no use,
and so are the doctors...

1062
02:26:48,160 --> 02:26:50,986
But when my lover came back...

1063
02:26:53,758 --> 02:26:58,884
if law wants proof,
then it is in front of you.

1064
02:26:59,942 --> 02:27:03,307
What are you saying Anand,
I haven't understood you.

1065
02:27:03,996 --> 02:27:13,783
If Madhavi appears in the 
garb of Madhu, like me...

1066
02:27:14,724 --> 02:27:18,161
...he too will think
Madhu has returned.

1067
02:27:18,511 --> 02:27:20,277
Then what will happen, Anand?

1068
02:27:20,633 --> 02:27:23,499
That coward will break
down in such a situation.

1069
02:27:23,635 --> 02:27:27,580
He will admit his crime,
and seek forgivance.

1070
02:27:29,309 --> 02:27:35,861
Madhavi, I request 
you, please help me.

1071
02:27:38,452 --> 02:27:39,452
Brother!

1072
02:27:42,072 --> 02:27:43,548
Then when do we act, Anand?

1073
02:27:43,769 --> 02:27:46,603
That I will return and tell you.

1074
02:27:49,110 --> 02:27:51,985
Inspector, are you with me?

1075
02:27:52,277 --> 02:27:54,676
To be with you is 
the duty of Law.

1076
02:27:55,096 --> 02:27:59,631
I will not forget your favor
till my death. I'll take leave.

1077
02:29:07,566 --> 02:29:10,760
You are sitting here?
- What are you doing here?

1078
02:29:12,316 --> 02:29:14,886
To apologise to you. - For what?

1079
02:29:16,558 --> 02:29:22,621
In youth, one makes many
mistakes and I did the same.

1080
02:29:23,516 --> 02:29:25,155
Tell me clearly, 
what do you want!

1081
02:29:26,220 --> 02:29:29,399
For Madhumati, I unnecessarily 
fought with you.

1082
02:29:30,183 --> 02:29:33,452
The result you see in front of you.
I have nothing to eat or wear.

1083
02:29:34,330 --> 02:29:35,621
I am fed up of life.

1084
02:29:36,164 --> 02:29:38,125
If you are fed up,
why have you come here?

1085
02:29:39,361 --> 02:29:42,062
If you help me, I will return home.

1086
02:29:45,584 --> 02:29:50,160
No I do not want money for free.
I will work for it.

1087
02:29:50,697 --> 02:29:52,312
You are still very proud.

1088
02:29:52,954 --> 02:29:55,535
If my pride was still there,
I wouldn't have come to you.

1089
02:29:56,301 --> 02:30:01,117
You know I make portraits,
I will make a portrait of you.

1090
02:30:02,666 --> 02:30:07,198
Your hobby of making pictures is
still there, but I don't have time.

1091
02:30:11,491 --> 02:30:17,741
I might not live to
come again Please help me.

1092
02:30:18,719 --> 02:30:22,463
I don't have time. - I will
come at whatever time you say.

1093
02:30:24,333 --> 02:30:26,671
Ok, you come tomorrow at
around 6 or 6:30 in the evening.

1094
02:30:28,078 --> 02:30:32,835
Thank you very much,
I will take leave.

1095
02:30:42,202 --> 02:30:46,352
Here, take this. Come tomorrow
at 8:OO in the evening to palace.

1096
02:30:48,099 --> 02:30:49,299
You will come?

1097
02:30:52,557 --> 02:30:55,357
This dress is exactly
like the one she wore...

1098
02:30:55,398 --> 02:30:57,167
...on that night.

1099
02:30:57,876 --> 02:31:02,658
Sir, you will come with
her tomorrow night? - Yes.

1100
02:31:02,896 --> 02:31:03,984
Ok, then I will make a move.

1101
02:31:04,108 --> 02:31:07,280
You have just come, have a cup 
of tea. Madhavi, a cup of tea.

1102
02:31:07,321 --> 02:31:12,854
No, no. Don't take the trouble.
I have a lot to do.

1103
02:31:13,774 --> 02:31:15,429
I can't stay for a minute.

1104
02:31:15,820 --> 02:31:19,007
But tomorrow, at 8 sharp.
Will you remember.

1105
02:31:19,351 --> 02:31:20,849
Yes, tomorrow, at 8 sharp.

1106
02:31:24,465 --> 02:31:25,465
Poor chap.

1107
02:31:37,414 --> 02:31:42,249
First I will go, all arrangements 
have been done. - Ok.

1108
02:32:10,692 --> 02:32:12,044
What a dreadful night!

1109
02:32:13,585 --> 02:32:15,457
You have come here to talk,
or to make a portrait!

1110
02:32:15,877 --> 02:32:17,349
Do your work.

1111
02:32:27,457 --> 02:32:30,248
Behind you! Whose shadow is that?

1112
02:32:36,598 --> 02:32:38,604
It is nothing, just the 
shadow of the curtain.

1113
02:32:41,058 --> 02:32:45,418
Did you try and scare me?
- I am myself scared.

1114
02:32:45,707 --> 02:32:47,938
I don't have time to waste.
What's the time?

1115
02:32:49,414 --> 02:32:51,874
There isn't much time 
left for 8 o'clock.

1116
02:32:52,053 --> 02:32:53,353
Go do your work.

1117
02:32:54,942 --> 02:32:55,605
Okay.

1118
02:32:58,845 --> 02:33:01,681
Rajasaheb, blood! - Blood?

1119
02:33:08,730 --> 02:33:09,930
Yes. See here!

1120
02:33:12,877 --> 02:33:15,687
There are blood spots which've
come up on your picture.

1121
02:33:16,458 --> 02:33:17,722
This must be your handiwork.

1122
02:33:17,806 --> 02:33:21,137
No, Rajasaheb, there is 
someone else's hand in it.

1123
02:33:21,498 --> 02:33:25,758
But besides us, there 
is no one else here.

1124
02:33:26,419 --> 02:33:31,520
There is somebody else here.
I can feel it. Did you hear it?

1125
02:33:31,994 --> 02:33:36,710
As if some one is softly entering.
Can you hear it?

1126
02:33:36,760 --> 02:33:38,534
No, I am not hearing anything.

1127
02:33:39,590 --> 02:33:40,939
Rub out those spots.

1128
02:34:07,758 --> 02:34:10,666
Are you afraid, Rajasaheb?
- Of course not!

1129
02:34:16,198 --> 02:34:17,610
What are you staring at me for?

1130
02:34:18,019 --> 02:34:19,712
What ever the artist sees.

1131
02:34:20,556 --> 02:34:24,619
What is inside,
he wants to portray that.

1132
02:34:25,300 --> 02:34:28,129
Rajasaheb, do you 
believe in spirits?

1133
02:34:28,315 --> 02:34:29,715
Why do you ask such a question?

1134
02:34:30,097 --> 02:34:34,648
The night is like that.
It appears some spirit...

1135
02:34:34,689 --> 02:34:39,786
...whose dreams are incomplete
is trying to enter here.

1136
02:34:42,091 --> 02:34:49,336
Those shadows, those 
terrifying sobs...- Enough!

1137
02:34:58,940 --> 02:35:02,199
Close the window!

1138
02:35:19,772 --> 02:35:21,205
Those footsteps!

1139
02:35:29,264 --> 02:35:31,995
Who is that? Anand, lights!

1140
02:35:54,192 --> 02:36:00,253
Don't come a step forward.
Go away from here. Get out.

1141
02:36:00,824 --> 02:36:02,676
Anand, tell her to 
get out of here.

1142
02:36:05,315 --> 02:36:09,722
Why should you be scared today.
Do you remember that stormy night?

1143
02:36:10,848 --> 02:36:15,777
You brought
me here on some false pretext!

1144
02:36:16,688 --> 02:36:21,329
What happened after that?
Speak, what happened?

1145
02:36:23,785 --> 02:36:24,785
Why are you quiet?

1146
02:36:25,789 --> 02:36:29,275
Halt, I will tell everything.

1147
02:36:30,151 --> 02:36:32,800
You came crying for sir,
into my room...

1148
02:36:34,012 --> 02:36:35,841
I tried to get hold of you.

1149
02:36:36,533 --> 02:36:41,178
But you slipped my hold and 
ran away. I followed you...

1150
02:37:21,861 --> 02:37:26,205
Halt there, if you come forward,
I will jump down from here.

1151
02:37:26,700 --> 02:37:30,033
You will never be able to get 
peace after killing an innocent.

1152
02:37:56,551 --> 02:38:00,133
Then you buried my body
near the stream...

1153
02:38:00,442 --> 02:38:04,904
...so that nobody will know.
- Yes, I had killed you.

1154
02:38:05,301 --> 02:38:07,135
And today I will kill you again.

1155
02:38:10,289 --> 02:38:12,963
Some body here? Lights, lights.

1156
02:38:18,487 --> 02:38:20,952
You are under arrest.
- All this is false.

1157
02:38:20,993 --> 02:38:24,797
I have heard all and you
just admitted to the murder.

1158
02:38:25,459 --> 02:38:27,532
Any clarifications you have,
you can give in the court.

1159
02:38:27,573 --> 02:38:28,769
Constable!

1160
02:38:31,929 --> 02:38:33,079
Take the gun.

1161
02:38:41,508 --> 02:38:47,345
That sinner will get punishment
for his crime, but so what?

1162
02:38:49,603 --> 02:38:51,064
But so what?

1163
02:38:53,654 --> 02:39:00,287
My peace will never return.
My peace can never return, Madhavi.

1164
02:39:05,513 --> 02:39:09,955
I am grateful to you.
Because of you...

1165
02:39:16,707 --> 02:39:18,720
But how did you know
all these things...

1166
02:39:20,973 --> 02:39:24,042
How did you know all those
things which I too didn't know.

1167
02:39:26,163 --> 02:39:30,505
After reaching this place, how did
you know what happened to Madhu?

1168
02:39:32,783 --> 02:39:35,135
Why are you smiling?

1169
02:39:36,852 --> 02:39:38,752
Why that strange
brightness in your eyes.

1170
02:39:39,733 --> 02:39:41,303
Where are you going Madhavi?

1171
02:39:44,880 --> 02:39:47,693
Brother, it is 8 o'clock.
I will go running.

1172
02:39:49,883 --> 02:39:53,529
Why are you quiet,
answer my questions.

1173
02:39:53,570 --> 02:39:55,765
Anil sir. Anil sir.

1174
02:39:57,577 --> 02:40:02,444
Sorry, I am late.
The car broke down on the way.

1175
02:40:05,133 --> 02:40:05,945
Madhu?

1176
02:40:06,979 --> 02:40:08,141
What happened?

1177
02:40:14,888 --> 02:40:17,483
Madhu had come. - Who?

1178
02:40:17,836 --> 02:40:20,726
Madhu. - But where is she?

1179
02:40:20,868 --> 02:40:21,657
Sir.

1180
02:40:22,267 --> 02:40:26,220
Heard it? She is calling me.

1181
02:40:26,571 --> 02:40:27,438
Sir.

1182
02:40:28,213 --> 02:40:29,414
She is calling me.

1183
02:40:30,476 --> 02:40:32,461
Anil sir. Anil sir.

1184
02:40:32,812 --> 02:40:33,883
Madhvi?

1185
02:40:34,789 --> 02:40:35,984
Sir.

1186
02:40:38,070 --> 02:40:40,039
Anil sir.

1187
02:40:42,242 --> 02:40:43,335
Madhu?

1188
02:40:48,365 --> 02:40:49,264
Sir.

1189
02:40:51,185 --> 02:40:53,279
Anil sir.

1190
02:40:54,498 --> 02:40:55,381
Madhu?

1191
02:40:55,802 --> 02:41:03,934
Come. Since long, I have 
been waiting for you.

1192
02:41:04,095 --> 02:41:10,740
My eyes are tired waiting...

1193
02:41:11,304 --> 02:41:21,789
Come, my foreigner!

1194
02:41:29,489 --> 02:41:32,346
And that is how my
last birth came to an end.

1195
02:41:33,161 --> 02:41:36,732
I did not get Madhu in that life.
At the time of death...

1196
02:41:36,773 --> 02:41:38,935
I had only one wish. One wish.

1197
02:41:40,212 --> 02:41:42,966
That in my next birth,
I'll get her back.

1198
02:41:44,373 --> 02:41:48,904
And in this life I have found 
her, Doctor! - Who? Radha?

1199
02:41:49,268 --> 02:41:58,318
Yes. Crossing death, we were 
born again. And we met again.

1200
02:42:00,879 --> 02:42:04,373
It is morning!
There is no sign of the driver.

1201
02:42:04,899 --> 02:42:07,586
Radha must have had a harrowing
time at the station waiting for us.

1202
02:42:07,764 --> 02:42:08,639
Sir.. Sir..

1203
02:42:08,680 --> 02:42:10,982
Has the road opened?
- Yes, it is open, but...

1204
02:42:11,023 --> 02:42:13,392
...there is some bad news.
The train in which Radha...

1205
02:42:13,433 --> 02:42:15,533
...was travelling has met with 
an accident. Many are injured.

1206
02:42:15,824 --> 02:42:16,650
How have you come to know?

1207
02:42:16,691 --> 02:42:18,422
People coming from
below are saying so.

1208
02:42:19,461 --> 02:42:21,611
It cannot happen! Come, doctor.

1209
02:43:07,017 --> 02:43:07,783
Radha.

1210
02:43:08,556 --> 02:43:10,767
Thank you, for coming back.

1211
